{"tid":1061647,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"根本話美c勁既都未睇過顛峰既球王李惠堂踢波","createTime":"2019-03-14T13:57:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T14:07:33.000Z","uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"639191a4ed80a32ffc062b70082061e2fe9fc670","tid":1061647,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T13:57:49.000Z","msg":"一：一腳踢死球迷？<br />\n<br />\n1931年，李惠堂到越南西貢對戰越南的比賽，當時因譚江柏與對方後衛互有動手，雙方球員衝突，甚至有球迷衝入球場，持木棍追打李惠堂，李惠堂起飛腳踢中對方下顎，該球迷院一個月後不治，李惠堂曾表示此事乃憾事。<br />\n<br />\n二：一球射死球員？<br />\n<br />\n1929年，李惠堂隨南華隊到印尼比賽，於對巴城聯的賽事中，李惠堂主射罰球，省中對方一名荷蘭球員（有說該球員用頭迎接李惠堂的球），導致該球員昏迷26小時，但並非如傳聞所說般去世。<br />\n<br />\n三：一球射穿網？<br />\n<br />\n1941年，李惠堂隨南華到馬拉出戰檳城軍聯隊，在大勝對方11球同時，李惠堂曾一腳射穿網，而其好友汪清澄接受訪問時曾說過，射穿網除了因李惠堂腳力好，亦因球網質素不佳。"},{"pid":"5a59a063d0cfc2e5349612404a69bf9ac7cb8835","tid":1061647,"uid":25022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T14:02:06.000Z","msg":"大力金剛腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a0466a6be4ca5a5f61e476e38e49377d094a3a","tid":1061647,"uid":10392,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T14:04:21.000Z","msg":"我朗都射穿過網<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d9U63A_pXVw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd9U63A_pXVw&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpi6Ol0HYJA13lVA%2BPgi6hPY%3D&h=7cc939ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d9U63A_pXVw</a>"},{"pid":"af013f9aa9e8de72056d1120dde41e5d2a8795ef","tid":1061647,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0a0466a6be4ca5a5f61e476e38e49377d094a3a","tid":1061647,"uid":10392,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T14:04:21.000Z","msg":"我朗都射穿過網<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d9U63A_pXVw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd9U63A_pXVw&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpi6Ol0HYJA13lVA%2BPgi6hPY%3D&h=7cc939ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d9U63A_pXVw</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T14:07:08.000Z","msg":"